Shameless nerf recap INC....<br>
<br>
- LifeTap/Dots changed<br>
- Added a Recast Time to Pact of Shadow<br>
- Removed Charm<br>
- Lots of spells removed (Beguile, Vampiric Wave, Removed Lifetap AE IV, Umbral<br>
Messenger)<br>
- Removed Corpse Bomb <br>
- Changed Voice Graft<br>
- LifeTaps changed based on level<br>
- DOTs changed based on movement<br>
- High Level (39+) Pets weakened<br>
- Pets no longer use Weapon delay<br>
- Pets no longer proc weapons<br>
- Made other spells a lot easier to resist (i.e., Darkness)<br>
- Removed stun effect of Ignite Bones<br>
- Changed Voice Graft<br>
- Screaming Terror does not cause mob to flee, as was originally intended<br>
- The &quot;Enhancement&quot; to Screaming Terror is still _worse_ that the way it was_supposed_ to work.<br>
